40
00:03:49,220 --> 00:03:50,130
I understand.

41
00:03:52,790 --> 00:03:55,550
Trusting someone is something very difficult.

42
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,380
Once I didn't believe that

43
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:02,140
people like me

44
00:04:02,630 --> 00:04:04,220
