56
00:04:45,790 --> 00:04:46,420
Madam,

57
00:04:47,030 --> 00:04:47,870
don't you trust that

58
00:04:48,330 --> 00:04:49,380
I could handle things well?

59
00:04:51,860 --> 00:04:52,510
Sister,

60
00:04:53,580 --> 00:04:54,950
are you really going to...

61
