78
00:05:37,940 --> 00:05:38,580
Okay?

79
00:05:39,860 --> 00:05:40,380
Okay.

80
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,420
We should have fun then.

81
00:05:50,780 --> 00:05:51,670
I have to go.

82
