Yunqing.

109
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:01,630
Don't scare me.

110
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:03,220
Yunqing, I'm here.

111
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:04,590
Imperial physician.

112
00:09:04,740 --> 00:09:05,220
Wan.

